trans-unit.source: Acquire a Twilio account and authentication token.

trans-unit.source: To get started with Twilio, sign up at <link><linkText>https://www.twilio.com/try-twilio[try_twilio]</linkText><title></title></link>.
trans-unit.target: To get started with Twilio, sign up at <link><linkText>https://www.twilio.com/try-twilio[try_twilio]</linkText><title></title></link>.

trans-unit.source: You can evaluate pricing at <link><linkText>http://www.twilio.com/pricing[twilio_pricing]</linkText><title></title></link>.
trans-unit.target: You can evaluate pricing at <link><linkText>http://www.twilio.com/pricing[twilio_pricing]</linkText><title></title></link>.

trans-unit.source: For information about the API provided by Twilio, see <link><linkText>http://www.twilio.com/voice/api[twilio_api]</linkText><title></title></link>.

trans-unit.source: Open your solution in Visual Studio.
trans-unit.target: Open your solution in Visual Studio.

trans-unit.source: Right-click References.
trans-unit.target: Right-click References.

trans-unit.source: Click Manage NuGet Packages.
trans-unit.target: Click Manage NuGet Packages.

trans-unit.source: Click Online.
trans-unit.target: Click Online.

trans-unit.source: In the search online box, type twilio.
trans-unit.target: In the search online box, type twilio.

trans-unit.source: Click Install on the Twilio package.
trans-unit.target: Click Install on the Twilio package.
